Ora confirmed the news, first reported by The Hollywood Reporter, on Twitter:

"Fifty Shades of Grey," which just began shooting Monday and arrives in theaters in February 2015, stars Dakota Johnson and Jamie Dornan as Anastasia Steele and Christian Grey.

